====Helping Spider-Man====
{{Quote|Harry! You find anything?"<br>"No. I mean, [[Unicorn|she]]'s referred to as 'a physically gifted athlete.'"<br>"You sure she's not a distant cousin of the [[Hulk/Norman Osborn-Mentored Spider-Man|Hulk]] or something?"<br>"Gotta be the [[Unicorn Helmet|helmet]]. I mean, the other villains you fought all had little upgrades, didn't they?|[[Spider-Man/Norman Osborn-Mentored Spider-Man|Spider-Man]] and Harry Osborn|The Unicorn Unleashed!}}
''To be added''

====Meeting Nico Minoru====
{{Quote|Sorry about the wait, it's a nightmare finding parking around here. Hey, thanks for letting me crash the movie. Oh, and nice to meet you, Nico.|Harry Osborn to [[Nico Minoru/Norman Osborn-Mentored Spider-Man|Nico Minoru]]|The Unicorn Unleashed!}}
''To be added'' 

====Hangout at the Parker Residence====
{{Quote|Your mom's an awesome chef."<br>"She's pretty great. But, uh, [[May Parker/Norman Osborn-Mentored Spider-Man|May]]'s actually my aunt. My [[Mary Parker/Norman Osborn-Mentored Spider-Man|mom]] passed away a while back."<br>"Oh. I'm sorry, I shouldn't have assumed. Hey, my [[Emily Osborn|mom]]'s not around anymore, either.|Harry Osborn and [[Spider-Man/Norman Osborn-Mentored Spider-Man|Peter Parker]]|Duel With the Devil}}
''To be added''

====Bonding with Nico Minoru====
{{Quote|Look, I know you wanna blame me for ruining everything, but the reality is, I'm not the one who kept all this a secret from you in the first place. Sorry. The truth is [[Spider-Man/Norman Osborn-Mentored Spider-Man|Peter]] is actually the first friend I've had in a while that wasn't trying to use me for money or likes. And if it makes you feel better, Peter didn't intentionally bring me on to team Spider-Man. I only found out because I was in the right place at the right time.|Harry Osborn to [[Nico Minoru/Norman Osborn-Mentored Spider-Man|Nico Minoru]]|Scorpion Rising}}
